extract or git-clone here other Vim plugins:

 * https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree.git
 * https://github.com/klen/python-mode.git (up to 0.4.0)

 * https://github.com/egirshov/jslint.vim.git
        (forked from https://github.com/hallettj/jslint.vim.git)

 * BufExplorer: http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=42

 * https://github.com/vim-scripts/errormarker.vim.git


  On Debian6, following additional packages should be installed:
    * vim-nox (or another 'extended' Vim compiled with Python support)
    * python-rope
